data.title: Dare by Philip Jose Farmer Ballantine 1965 First Print
data.meta_description:
See pics for condition. Preowned.


Explore the realm of science fiction with Philip Jose Farmer's Dare, a novel set in a futuristic world filled with fantasy and adventure. Published by Ballantine Books in 1965, this paperback edition is a rare first print that's a must-have for any book collector.


The pages of this gripping narrative will transport you to a new world where anything is possible. Immerse yourself in a tale of futurism and fantasy, as you follow the journey of the protagonist through an exciting and imaginative plot. Don't miss the chance to own this extraordinary piece of literature that will captivate your imagination from start to finish.
